g is when a Jeet calls for service and asks him the price, and then tells him that he is too expensive.</p>\n<p>He said, so not only does he get all White Customers, but the Jeets turn themselves away on price alone. At least the ones not worth dealing with anyhow.</p>\n<p>So you see, you just need to adapt. It never matters what a Government does, you can always find a way between the cracks.</p>\n<p>Buddy says, what are they going to do, close him down for having almost all White customers??</p>\n<p>Smart Dude. He used to work in corporate IT until they tried to make him Train his Jeet replacement.</p>\n", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 5, "score_up": 25, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "text", "uuid": "1ASZR0jy5K", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 27, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8561572, "raw_content": "As an avid concert goer, this is a big win. I have essentially been priced out of the market to take my family to a show. Yes, I am not with Trump on this one.", "author": "Mega_MAGA", "created": 1776300936146, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "kek-is-tan", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "", "removal_source": "", "link": "", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "Fuck You Ticketmaster ", "last_comment_created": 1776305001036, "content": "<p>As an avid concert goer, this is a big win. I have essentially been priced out of the market to take my family to a show. Yes, I am not with Trump on 